{"type": "article", "id": 14716, "title": "无线音响", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-10T06:49:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606060003215Rkrc6Z8AMJ2hD31.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t丹麦视听品牌 Bang &amp; Olufsen(B&amp;O) 发布最新无线音箱“ beoplay A6”。略有弯曲的外形像一片叶子，最大化放出声音。外面包裹着纯手工制造的 kvadrat 羊毛混纺面料，有很好的穿透力，也可以替换浅灰，深灰，黑玫瑰，藏青色等几种颜色，非常适合放在家里。使用时只需上下滑动，就可以调整音响的播放音量了。产品即将出售，<a href=\"http://www.bang-olufsen.com/zh\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142202oWXBs4vf76beMhUz.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"551\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67359413\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142202gVHOf7kMpqwyhdWF.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"511\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.62469438\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142203vxzl7qJfT3VGNQOE.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"517\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.63202934\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142203l7QzMuU6FntDLjiy.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"817\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.99877751\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142204gKEz3dicpR5jfuaD.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"944\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.15403423\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}